The paper discusses the release of a dataset for research on modeling user listening and interaction behavior in streaming, as well as Music Information Retrieval (MIR), and session-based sequential recommendations. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Sound and Music Computing (cs.SD), Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Multimedia (cs.MM).
